nodes.text: Transport ships of this unidentified class were used at the time of the Galactic Civil War. This class had an elongated body with a bridge section in the bow and outriggers extending from the stern section on both sides.
Among the organizations using this starship class were the Dynath Miners in the Bright Jewel system.
The Royal Naboo Security Forces used those transports as deep space scanners in the Naboo system.

Ships of this unidentified class could be found in all space sectors of Sony Online Entertainment's MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. Most served no purpose and randomly flew around in the game's space zones. A few ships were used during space quests, mostly involving patrols and rescue operations. The class was only identified as "Civilian Transport".
